member.remark:
To write to extraction fields without doing bUpdateFile, like "Adept/Libcard/Right Click Menu/Override Rights/Edit Extraction Fields.
Call WritePrivateProfileString("Adept", "UserNowCanEditAttributes", "T", NxLogin.SystemIniFilePNE);
before calling BatchUpdate, and
Call WritePrivateProfileString("Adept", "UserNowCanEditAttributes", "F", NxLogin.SystemIniFilePNE);
after.

